<i>noun</i>: 반동 [반ː동] <i>verb</i>: 흠칫흠칫하다 [흠치틈치타다], 흠칫하다 [흠치타다], 흠칫대다 [흠칟때다], 흠칫거리다 [흠칟꺼리다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>반동 [반ː동]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rebound; recoil</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 힘이나 움직임에 대하여 그 반대로 움직임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of moving against a certain force or movement.</dd><br>
<dd>2. reactionary; conservative</dd><br>
<dd>진보나 개혁 또는 혁신의 움직임을 반대하거나 가로막음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of opposing or obstructing a liberal, reformative, or innovative movement.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>흠칫흠칫하다 [흠치틈치타다]</dt><br>
<dd>recoil; flinch</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움츠리며 자꾸 갑자기 놀라다.</dd><br>
<dd>To shrink suddenly, repeatedly with fright.</dd><br>
<dt>흠칫하다 [흠치타다]</dt><br>
<dd>recoil; flinch</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움츠리며 갑자기 놀라다.</dd><br>
<dd>To shrink suddenly with fright.</dd><br>
<dt>흠칫대다 [흠칟때다]</dt><br>
<dd>recoil; flinch</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움츠리며 갑자기 자꾸 놀라다.</dd><br>
<dd>To shrink suddenly, repeatedly with fright.</dd><br>
<dt>흠칫거리다 [흠칟꺼리다]</dt><br>
<dd>recoil; flinch</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움츠리며 갑자기 자꾸 놀라다.</dd><br>
<dd>To shrink suddenly, repeatedly with fright.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>